  "keyFeatures": [
    "Supports 8-bit AVR and 32-bit ARM microcontrollers via Hardware Abstraction Layer (HAL)",
    "Comprehensive G-code command set for motion, temperature, bed leveling, and calibration",
    "Automatic bed leveling (Bilinear, UBL, Mesh) for improved print quality",
    "Multi-extruder support with up to 8 extruders and 9 coordinated axes",
    "Power-loss recovery to resume prints after power failure",
    "Filament runout sensor support",
    "Wide LCD and display controller support",
    "TMC stepper driver integration with StealthChop and CoolStep",
    "Built-in simulator for Windows, macOS, and Linux",
    "PlatformIO and Arduino IDE build system support"
  ],
